apps.localizedDescription:
Facebook is a website and app where people can connect with friends and family, share photos, videos, and updates about their lives, and see what others are doing. 

It’s also used to join groups, follow news, and find events or businesses.
apps.name: Facebook Wolf NoAds
apps.subtitle: Tweak v2.1 - v1.3

apps.localizedDescription:
Instagram is a website and app where people mainly share photos and videos about their life, hobbies, or work. It’s a place to show what you’re doing, what you like, or what you create. 

People also follow others — like friends, celebrities, or brands — to see their pictures and videos.
apps.name: Instagram Regram
apps.subtitle: Tweak v1.0.29

apps.localizedDescription:
Reddit is a website and app where people talk about anything by posting questions, stories, pictures, or news. 

 It’s like a huge collection of little communities (called subreddits) where each one is about a different topic — like movies, sports, funny memes, advice, or hobbies.
apps.name: Reddit Filter
apps.subtitle: Tweak v1.1.7

apps.localizedDescription:
TikTok is an app where people make, watch, and share short videos, usually with music, fun effects, or funny moments. 

It’s mostly used for entertainment, like dancing, jokes, challenges, or quick tips.
apps.name: TikTok Vibe
apps.subtitle: Tweak v1.2

apps.localizedDescription:
WhatsApp is an app where people can send messages, make calls, send photos, videos, and voice messages to each other using the internet. 

 It’s mainly for talking with friends, family, or groups easily and for free, without using regular text messaging or phone call minutes.
apps.name: Whatsapp Watusi
apps.subtitle: Tweak v1.2.70

apps.localizedDescription:
X (which used to be called Twitter) is a website and app where people post short messages, called posts or tweets, to share thoughts, news, jokes, or updates quickly. 

People use it to talk about what’s happening right now, follow news, join conversations, and see what famous people or brands are saying.
apps.name: X BH
apps.subtitle: Tweak v4.4

apps.localizedDescription:
YouTube is a website and app where people watch, upload, and share videos. 

You can find videos about anything — like music, tutorials, funny clips, news, gaming, or shows. People use YouTube to learn, be entertained, or share their own videos with the world.
apps.name: Youtube Plus
apps.subtitle: Tweak v5.2b1
